DESCRIPTION:Bring the family to the Cordry‑Sweetwater Easter Egg Hunt on April 4 from 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. at the Cordry‑Sweetwater Fire Department in Nineveh. This free community event features four separate egg‑hunting areas for different age groups, snacks for kids, and a special visit from the Easter Bunny—perfect fun for all ages.\n
