SUMMARY:Friends of the Library Annual Plant Sale
DESCRIPTION:Spring is here and it’s time for the annual Friends of the Library Plant Sale! Featuring a wide variety of landscaping plants, including native varieties, you are sure to find something to add to your home.\nBrown County Soil and Water will also be giving away free tree saplings, while they last.\n\nThe sale will be held RAIN OR SHINE under the solar panels in the lower parking lot at the end of East Gould Street\nCash, check or card accepted\nNo pre-sales\nAll proceeds support Friends of the Library projects to benefit the Brown County Public Library\n\n
