SUMMARY:Easter Brunch at Story Inn
DESCRIPTION:Breakfast served with Following: Creamy Heirloom Cheesy Grits, Story Fries, Bacon, and Sausage.\n\nCrab Cakes Benedict with Creamy Dill infused Hollandaise\nVanilla Bean French Toast Casserole served with Vanilla Bean Ice Cream and Maple Syrup\nThick Cut Ham Steak with Scramble Eggs\nFresh Strawberry Salad and Grilled Chicken Balsamic Dressing\nClassic BAG’s\nFrench inspired Quiche Lorraine\n\nOnly $25 Per Person\nCall 812-988-2273 for reservations\n
