SUMMARY:Journal Cover Collage Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Dive into this low-stakes, high-reward workshop and create your own expressive collage with the guidance of local artist Abby Moses. Design your own sketchbook or journal cover with our selection of memerobilia including old magazines, photography books, stickers, and paint markers and learn some helpful techniques to craft your own personalized collage. Feel free to bring your own scraps to include if you’d like, as well! \nThis approachable workshop is good for anyone, regardless of skill level– even the most timid creatives can channel their inner artst and create a unique and impactful work of art. Abby will walk you through techniques and approaches to help you create a fun and expressive collage while you enjoy Second Story Studio’s cozy studio space.\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/journal-cover-collage-workshop/
