SUMMARY:Egg Decorating Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a relaxing Friday night with friends and family, wood burning, painting, or marbling paper mache eggs. Make a special egg for your Easter centerpiece or to give in an Easter basket.\nJoin us Fridays for our SPRING WORKSHOPS! Book Friday, Apr. 3 to May 29, 6PM to 8PM. Your project price includes one beverage; wine, beer, coffee, espresso, hot chocolate or tea (other selections are available) Ages 15+\nSeats limited. You must book ahead.\nYou must be 21+ to consume alcohol.\n
