SUMMARY:(American) Pomp!: Trumpet, Piano, Winds, and Strings
DESCRIPTION:ChamberFest Brown County presents (American) Pomp!\nA flamboyant end to festival week: a program of genre-bending and jazz-inspired classics, culminating in Gershwin’s iconic Rhapsody in Blue!\nSaint-Saëns: Septet for Trumpet, Piano and Strings, op. 65\nMartinů: La Revue de Cuisine\nGershwin: Rhapsody in Blue\nArtists:​​\n\n​​​​Spencer Myer, piano soloist\nAndreas Ioannides, piano\nQing Hou, violin\nLei Hou, violin\nLarry Neuman, viola\nCaleb Wong, cello\nJim Campbell, clarinet\nMark Ridenour, trumpet\nVince Karamanov, bassoon\nAlex Horton, bass\n\n
