SUMMARY:Easter Buffet at Brown County Inn
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Easter Sunday at the Brown County Inn with a festive Easter Buffet on April 5, 2026. Start the day with a breakfast buffet from 8–10 AM featuring classic favorites like scrambled eggs, bacon, biscuits and gravy, hash brown casserole, French toast, and fresh fruit. The celebration continues with a brunch buffet with seatings at 11:30 AM, 1 PM, and 3 PM, offering carved ham and roast beef, salmon, shrimp cocktail, mac and cheese, vegetables, breakfast favorites, and a full soup and salad bar. An assortment of desserts and beverages completes the meal, and reservations are recommended by calling 812-988-2291.\n
