SUMMARY:Easter Brunch at Hard Truth
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Easter at Hard Truth Distilling Co. with a relaxed, open‑seating brunch experience in the House of Rye. Gather with family and friends and enjoy the rustic charm, wooded surroundings, and signature Hard Truth hospitality that make events here unforgettable.\nPair your meal with handcrafted cocktails or sips from the mimosa bar, then enjoy a stroll through the distillery grounds as you continue your Easter celebration.\nBrunch buffet includes:\nGlazed ham carving station\nLamb chops\nMini quiches\nHam & cheese croissant\nSpring pea salad\nDinner rolls\nChef’s choice vegetables\nRoasted Potatoes\nPasta salad\nAssorted desserts\nIced tea, lemonade, and water\nHandcrafted cocktails and mimosa bar will be available for additional purchase.\nBuffet is all ages; must be 21+ to purchase and consume alcohol.\nSeating is limited, so make your reservation today.\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/easter-brunch/
ORGANIZER;CN=Hard Truth Distilling Co.:MAILTO:events@bwqoht.com
