SUMMARY:Happy Hollow Children’s Camp Homeschool Day
DESCRIPTION:Families can take part in organized experiences such as the Zap Line, slingshot range, archery, arts and crafts, and more. Lunch is provided for all participants. Homeschool Day offers a meaningful opportunity for children to socialize with peers, engage in experiential learning, and enjoy the outdoors—while parents connect, share ideas, and build community.\n
