TRANSP:OPAQUE
SUMMARY:War in the Woods
DESCRIPTION: Get ready for one of the wildest, most adrenaline-charged drag-racing events in the country — War in the Woods No Prep, held at Brown County Dragway in Morgantown, Indiana. Twice each year, the speed-obsessed and the curious come together for a full throttle weekend of no-prep racing action and high-stakes competition. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+2Brown County Indiana+2\n📅 Upcoming Dates (2026):\n\n\nMay 29–30\n\n\nSeptember 18–19 war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\n📍 Location:Brown County Dragway — 480 Gatesville Road, Morgantown, IN 46160 Brown County Indiana+1\nWhat to Expect:\n\n\n⚡ High-octane drag races across multiple classes like Small Tire, Big Tire, Hard Tire, Stick Shift, Nitroous Mayhem and more. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\n🔊 Drivers meetings, chip draws, and a track that goes “hot” at 3:00 p.m. both days — expect action and intensity from start to finish. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\n🚗 A raw “no prep” setup for daring street cars, where traction is minimal and every run is a gamble — it’s what makes War in the Woods the wildest in the sport. No Prep Racing+1\n\n\n🎟️ General admission tickets available at the gate (cash only): $25 for one-day or $40 for a two-day pass. VIP packages (when available) offer perks like premium parking, food/drink vouchers, and exclusive access. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nImportant for Spectators:\n\n\nBring a chair — spectator seating is limited and mostly standing or informal. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nNo overnight camping or motorized spectator vehicles allowed — plan accordingly. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nParking is assigned on arrival; please follow staff directions — blocking driveways or track access will result in towing. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/warn-in-the-woods/
CATEGORIES:Entertainment,Happening,Outdoor Adventure,Races
LOCATION:480 Gatesville Road, Morgantown, IN 46160
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://browncounty.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Square-Images-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
