SUMMARY:Fall Volunteer Weekend
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a weekend at Waycross helping to start new projects as well as with ongoing efforts around our facility! We’ll offer a variety of work for all skill levels. Bring your passion and talent for a fun, active, community filled weekend.\nVolunteer Weekends are free and include meals and lodging. Registration is required so that we can make enough food to feed everyone!!\n\n\nSeptember 25-27, 2026\n\n\nCheck-in: 4-6pm\n\n\nCheck-out: 11:30am\n\n\n\n\nAll ages welcome, minors must be accompanied by an adult.\n\n\nAccommodation options:\n\n\nMain House/Sleeping Wing – Multi-Occupancy\n\n\nCabins – Multi-Occupancy\n\n\nCommuter – Come work with the crew on Saturday only (lunch provided)\n\n\n\n\n
