SUMMARY:Spring Nature Retreat: Blossoms & Bird Songs
DESCRIPTION:Set against the backdrop of blooming wildflowers and birdsongs, this peaceful retreat will offer a mix of guided nature walks, hands-on nature-inspired crafts, and simple seasonal activities for individuals and families of all ages. This weekend is about soaking up the sights and sounds of nature. We invite you to breathe deeply, play freely, and make memories rooted in wonder.\n\n\nApril 24-26, 2026\n\n\nCheck-in: 4-6pm\n\n\nCheck-out: 10am\n\n\n\n\nAll ages welcome, minors must be accompanied by an adult.\n\n\nProgram Rates\n\n\nAttendance cost is calculated during online registration, depending on your lodging selection. Rates are per person and include program fees, lodging and meals.\n\n\nMain House/Sleeping Wing – Multi-Occupancy: $210 per person\n\n\nMain House/Sleeping Wing – Single Occupancy: $280 per person\n\n\nCabin – Multi-Occupancy: $170 per person\n\n\nYouth (10-17): $150 per person\n\n\nChildren (4-9): $110 per person\n\n\n3 and under: $0\n\n\n\n\n\n\n
